{"tid":1523893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我係分化撚]你而家好嬲呀？咁你肯入機場、跳閘同罷工未呀？","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:52:06.000Z","uid":25250,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a859a4b82febdba7f3fc246336476411426e9337","tid":1523893,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:20:59.000Z","msg":"剩係識係FB 連登share 圖同片，有手有腳都識做啦<br />\n咁你地肯做實質行動未呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">接受現實啦，我地而家根本要脅唔到政權</span></span><br />\n我唔要求個個做勇武衝擊防線玩火魔法<br />\n但係每個人都要比以前行多一步，如果唔係，我地只會一齊輸"},{"pid":"39bda427c28b5e249bcdb1e1e7da07ff47c414aa","tid":1523893,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:22:32.000Z","msg":"係啵，唔記得連登仔全部都係鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f764527a4c6091e057e46fbb101ba76b933cb5fc","tid":1523893,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83cfd7fdf506685d25401230c01be7dd16dccb6c","tid":1523893,"uid":25250,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f764527a4c6091e057e46fbb101ba76b933cb5fc","tid":1523893,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:23:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:25:21.000Z","msg":"唔罷工無問題<br />\n咪等送中條例正式通過囉"},{"pid":"89fdb51cbb6d4c3567bcca33be92c06b167b8855","tid":1523893,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:26:36.000Z","msg":"推 同我岩岩個post一樣"},{"pid":"8d1477feddb2eb4bcdf26b60ed169d76715980f9","tid":1523893,"uid":153894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"今晚真係太嬲<br />\n點都罷！"},{"pid":"05740cdb4f4fe994330cd245835433a59b88cf3b","tid":1523893,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89fdb51cbb6d4c3567bcca33be92c06b167b8855","tid":1523893,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl